summary.title: Noregs konunga sǫgur, Vol III
summary.note: This manuscript, containing Ólafs saga helga is the second volume of a copy in three volumes, with AM 35 fol. as vol I and AM 36 fol. as vol I, Ásgeir Jónsson made of Kringla (Codex Academicus primus), which was destroyed in the Copenhagen fire of 1728. An electronic edition of the manuscript can be accessed at Menota's home page.
